@h1 Volunteer
@img.fr_top_right src=^girl2.jpg

@p
Freiker loves its volunteers.  We can usually use assistance with marketing, fundraising, and school operations and support, among other things, and our participating schools often have a need for additional volunteers.
@a href="../schools">Click here
to see if there is a local school where you can help out.
@p
Please use our contact form to let us know how you would like to help.  Please include your areas of interest and a description of any special skills that you have.
